      <p class="eye">Our Vision</p>
      <h2 class="stitle" style="margin-bottom:1rem;">A catalyst for spiritual awakening in Millcreek.</h2>
      <p style="color:var(--text-muted);margin-bottom:1rem;">In Acts 1:8, Jesus said, "You will be My witnesses both in Jerusalem, and in all Judea and Samaria, and even to the remotest parts of the earth." That begins right here in Millcreek, Utah.</p>
      <p style="color:var(--text-muted);margin-bottom:1.5rem;">As water flows to fill every low place, we are called to pour the Gospel into every corner of our community — through prayer, service, and the proclamation of Jesus Christ.</p>
      <div class="crystal-box" style="margin-bottom:1.5rem;">
        <h4>Mission Statement</h4>
        <p style="font-family:Merriweather,serif;font-size:1.05rem;font-weight:700;color:var(--blue-deep);margin-top:.4rem;">Love God. Love People. Share Jesus. Make Disciples.</p>
        <p style="font-size:.83rem;color:var(--text-muted);margin-top:.4rem;">From Matthew 22:38–39 and Matthew 28:19–20.</p>
      </div>
      <a class="btn btn-blue" href="pastor.html">Meet Our Pastor</a>
    </div><img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1505228395891-9a51e7e86bf6?auto=format&fit=crop&q=80&w=800" alt="Ocean — God's glory in creation" style="width:100%;height:420px;object-fit:cover;" class="reveal"/></div>
  </div>
</section>
<section class="sec ocean-sec" style="background:var(--blue-deep);">
  <div class="sec-inner">
    <p class="eye eye-lt eye-ctr reveal">What We Value</p>
    <h2 class="stitle stitle-lt reveal" style="text-align:center;margin-bottom:2.5rem;">Our Five Core Values</h2>
    <div class="card-grid-3">
<div class="crystal-card reveal">
  <h3>Intimacy With Jesus</h3>
  <p>Pursuing a passionate relationship with Jesus above all — in prayer, worship, and daily life.</p>
</div>
<div class="crystal-card reveal">
  <h3>Biblical Truth</h3>
  <p>Treasuring God's perfect, inerrant Word as our supreme standard for life, faith, and practice.</p>
</div>
<div class="crystal-card reveal">
  <h3>Intentional Hospitality</h3>
  <p>Welcoming every person with the unconditional love of Jesus — as the ocean welcomes every river.</p>
</div>
<div class="crystal-card reveal">
  <h3>Ministry Excellence</h3>
  <p>Reflecting the character of God in service — doing all things as unto the Lord.</p>
</div>
<div class="crystal-card reveal">
  <h3>City Renewal</h3>
  <p>Investing in the redemption of the people of Millcreek — one life, one family at a time.</p>
</div></div>
  </div></section>
